commit.message:
libscidavis/CMakeLists.txt: fix build if sip-4 installed.

If sip-4 is installed as well as sip-6 /usr/include/pythonX.Y/sip.h
from sip-4 overwrites the sip.h generated by sip-6. We fix this
by specifying BEFORE when we include the sip-6 sip.h.

Signed-off-by: Andrew Ammerlaan <andrewammerlaan@gentoo.org>

libscidavis/CMakeLists.txt: fix build if sip-4 installed.

If sip-4 is installed as well as sip-6 /usr/include/pythonX.Y/sip.h
from sip-4 overwrites the sip.h generated by sip-6. We fix this
by specifying BEFORE when we include the sip-6 sip.h.

Signed-off-by: Andrew Ammerlaan <andrewammerlaan@gentoo.org>
